General.Name: Copper Search Ltd
General.Description: Copper Search Limited engages in the exploration of minerals exploration tenements located in South Australia. Its flagship project includes the Peake Project that comprises copper-gold deposits covering an area of 5,560 square kilometers located in the Northern Gawler Craton, South Australia. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Magill, Australia.
